Robert Livingston (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Livingston_(actor) 0 Robert Edward Randall (December 9, 1904 – March 7, 1988) was an American film actor known under his stage name as Bob Livingston. He appeared in 135 films between 1921 and 1975. He was one of the original Three Mesquiteers. He had also played The Lone Ranger and Zorro.
